CREATE TABLE [Categories] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [Name] nvarchar(100) NOT NULL,
    [IsActive] bit NOT NULL,
    [ParentCategoryId] int NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Categories] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Categories_Categories_ParentCategoryId] FOREIGN KEY ([ParentCategoryId]) REFERENCES [Categories] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [Coupons] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [Name] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [Description] nvarchar(250) NULL,
    [Code] nvarchar(30) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Coupons] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Users] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [FirstName] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [LastName] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [Email] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [EmailConfirmed] bit NOT NULL,
    [PasswordHashed] nvarchar(128) NOT NULL,
    [PhoneNumber] nvarchar(11) NOT NULL,
    [PhoneNumberConfirmed] bit NOT NULL,
    [LockoutEnd] datetime2 NULL,
    [LockoutEnabled] bit NOT NULL,
    [AccessFailedCount] int NOT NULL,
    [CreatedOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [IsDeleted] bit NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Users] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Cities] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL,
    [NameAr] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [NameEn] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [GovernorateId] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Cities] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Cities_Governorates_GovernorateId] FOREIGN KEY ([GovernorateId]) REFERENCES [Governorates] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [Orders] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [OrderDate] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [TotalAmount] decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
    [Status] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Orders] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Orders_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [Products] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [Name] nvarchar(500) NOT NULL,
    [Description] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [IsActive] bit NOT NULL,
    [BrandId] int NOT NULL,
    [CategoryId] int NOT NULL,
    [CreatedByUserId] int NOT NULL,
    [CreatedOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [LastModifiedByUserId] int NULL,
    [LastModifiedOn] datetime2 NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Products] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Brands_BrandId] FOREIGN KEY ([BrandId]) REFERENCES [Brands] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Categories_CategoryId] FOREIGN KEY ([CategoryId]) REFERENCES [Categories] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Users_CreatedByUserId] FOREIGN KEY ([CreatedByUserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Users_LastModifiedByUserId] FOREIGN KEY ([LastModifiedByUserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [RefreshTokens] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [Token] nvarchar(100) NOT NULL,
    [ExpiresOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [IsUsed] bit NOT NULL,
    [IsRevoked] bit NOT NULL,
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [CreatedOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [CreatedByIp] nvarchar(50) NULL,
    [RevokedByIp] nvarchar(50) NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_RefreshTokens] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RefreshTokens_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [UserRoles] (
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [RoleId] int NOT NULL,
    [AssignedOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_UserRoles] PRIMARY KEY ([UserId], [RoleId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_UserRoles_Roles_RoleId] FOREIGN KEY ([RoleId]) REFERENCES [Roles] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_UserRoles_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [Addresses] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [CityId] int NOT NULL,
    [PostalCode] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [AddressDetails] nvarchar(500) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Addresses] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Addresses_Cities_CityId] FOREIGN KEY ([CityId]) REFERENCES [Cities] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Addresses_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [Payments] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [OrderId] int NOT NULL,
    [Amount] decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
    [Method] int NOT NULL,
    [Status] int NOT NULL,
    [PaymentDate] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Payments] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Payments_Orders_OrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [ProductInventories] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [ProductId] int NOT NULL,
    [IsActive] bit NOT NULL,
    [IsDigital] bit NOT NULL,
    [Price] decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
    [Weight] real NOT NULL,
    [UnitsInStock] int NOT NULL,
    [CreatedByUserId] int NOT NULL,
    [CreatedOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [LastModifiedByUserId] int NULL,
    [LastModifiedOn] datetime2 NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_ProductInventories] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_ProductInventories_Products_ProductId] FOREIGN KEY ([ProductId]) REFERENCES [Products] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_ProductInventories_Users_CreatedByUserId] FOREIGN KEY ([CreatedByUserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_ProductInventories_Users_LastModifiedByUserId] FOREIGN KEY ([LastModifiedByUserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Reviews] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [ProductId] int NOT NULL,
    [UserId] int NOT NULL,
    [Comment] nvarchar(1000) NULL,
    [Rating] tinyint NOT NULL,
    [CreatedOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Reviews] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Reviews_Products_ProductId] FOREIGN KEY ([ProductId]) REFERENCES [Products] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Reviews_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [Shippings] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [OrderId] int NOT NULL,
    [AddressId] int NOT NULL,
    [Status] int NOT NULL,
    [Method] int NOT NULL,
    [ShippedDate] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [DeliveryDate] datetime2 NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Shippings] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Shippings_Addresses_AddressId] FOREIGN KEY ([AddressId]) REFERENCES [Addresses] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Shippings_Orders_OrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [Discounts] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [ProductInventoryId] int NOT NULL,
    [Name] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [DiscountValue] int NOT NULL,
    [Start] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [End] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [IsActive] bit NOT NULL DEFAULT CAST(1 AS bit),
    [DiscountTypeId] int NOT NULL,
    [CouponId] int NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Discounts] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Discounts_Coupons_CouponId] FOREIGN KEY ([CouponId]) REFERENCES [Coupons] ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Discounts_DiscountTypes_DiscountTypeId] FOREIGN KEY ([DiscountTypeId]) REFERENCES [DiscountTypes] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Discounts_ProductInventories_ProductInventoryId] FOREIGN KEY ([ProductInventoryId]) REFERENCES [ProductInventories] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [OrderItems] (
    [OrderId] int NOT NULL,
    [ProductInventoryId] int NOT NULL,
    [Quantity] int NOT NULL,
    [Price] decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_OrderItems] PRIMARY KEY ([OrderId], [ProductInventoryId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_OrderItems_Orders_OrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_OrderItems_ProductInventories_ProductInventoryId] FOREIGN KEY ([ProductInventoryId]) REFERENCES [ProductInventories] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [ProductAttributeValues] (
    [AttributeId] int NOT NULL,
    [ProductInventoryId] int NOT NULL,
    [value] nvarchar(255) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_ProductAttributeValues] PRIMARY KEY ([ProductInventoryId], [AttributeId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_ProductAttributeValues_ProductAttributes_AttributeId] FOREIGN KEY ([AttributeId]) REFERENCES [ProductAttributes] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_ProductAttributeValues_ProductInventories_ProductInventoryId] FOREIGN KEY ([ProductInventoryId]) REFERENCES [ProductInventories] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [ProductInventoryImages] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [ProductInventoryId] int NOT NULL,
    [ImagePath] nvarchar(255) NULL,
    [DisplayOreder] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_ProductInventoryImages] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_ProductInventoryImages_ProductInventories_ProductInventoryId] FOREIGN KEY ([ProductInventoryId]) REFERENCES [ProductInventories] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [ShoppingCartItems] (
    [ShoppingCartId] int NOT NULL,
    [ProductInventoryId] int NOT NULL,
    [Quantity] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_ShoppingCartItems] PRIMARY KEY ([ShoppingCartId], [ProductInventoryId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_ShoppingCartItems_ProductInventories_ProductInventoryId] FOREIGN KEY ([ProductInventoryId]) REFERENCES [ProductInventories] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_ShoppingCartItems_ShoppingCarts_ShoppingCartId] FOREIGN KEY ([ShoppingCartId]) REFERENCES [ShoppingCarts] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [WishListItems] (
    [WishListId] int NOT NULL,
    [ProductInventoryId] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_WishListItems] PRIMARY KEY ([WishListId], [ProductInventoryId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_WishListItems_ProductInventories_ProductInventoryId] FOREIGN KEY ([ProductInventoryId]) REFERENCES [ProductInventories] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_WishListItems_WishLisits_WishListId] FOREIGN KEY ([WishListId]) REFERENCES [WishLisits] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [Categories] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [Name] nvarchar(100) NOT NULL,

    CONSTRAINT [FK_Categories_Categories_ParentCategoryId] FOREIGN KEY ([ParentCategoryId]) REFERENCES [Categories] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [Coupons] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [Name] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [Description] nvarchar(250) NULL,
    [Code] nvarchar(30) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Coupons] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Users] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [FirstName] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [LastName] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [Email] nvarchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [HashedPassword] nvarchar(128) NOT NULL,
    [PhoneNumber] nvarchar(11) NOT NULL,
    [CreatedOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [IsDeleted] bit NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Users] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Orders] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [UserId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [OrderDate] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [TotalAmount] decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
    [Status] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Orders] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Orders_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [Products] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [Name] nvarchar(500) NOT NULL,
    [Description] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    [IsActive] bit NOT NULL,
    [BrandId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [CategoryId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [CreatedByUserId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [CreatedOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [LastModifiedByUserId] uniqueidentifier NULL,
    [LastModifiedOn] datetime2 NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Products] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Brands_BrandId] FOREIGN KEY ([BrandId]) REFERENCES [Brands] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Categories_CategoryId] FOREIGN KEY ([CategoryId]) REFERENCES [Categories] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Users_CreatedByUserId] FOREIGN KEY ([CreatedByUserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Products_Users_LastModifiedByUserId] FOREIGN KEY ([LastModifiedByUserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [RefreshTokens] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [UserId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [Token] nvarchar(250) NOT NULL,
    [ExpiresOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [IsRevoked] bit NOT NULL,
    [CreatedOn] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_RefreshTokens] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_RefreshTokens_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [UserRoles] (

    CONSTRAINT [FK_UserRoles_Roles_RoleId] FOREIGN KEY ([RoleId]) REFERENCES [Roles] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_UserRoles_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [Payments] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [OrderId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [Amount] decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
    [Method] int NOT NULL,
    [Status] int NOT NULL,
    [PaymentDate] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Payments] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Payments_Orders_OrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [Shippings] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [OrderId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [AddressId] int NOT NULL,
    [Status] int NOT NULL,
    [Method] int NOT NULL,
    [ShippedDate] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [DeliveryDate] datetime2 NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Shippings] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Shippings_Orders_OrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [ProductInventories] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [ProductId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [IsActive] bit NOT NULL,
    [IsDigital] bit NOT NULL,
    [Price] decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
    [Weight] real NOT NULL,
    [UnitsInStock] int NOT NULL,

    CONSTRAINT [FK_ProductInventories_Users_LastModifiedByUserId] FOREIGN KEY ([LastModifiedByUserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Reviews] (
    [Id] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
